    dc:creator "Pádua, Diego G.; Araujo, Rodrigo O.; Mazariegos, Luis A." ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "Pimpla Fabricius (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Pimplinae) from Colombia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3479051>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3479056>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3479053> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3479051>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1. A–C: Pimpla Fabricius species newly recorded to Colombia (in vivo—lateral view). A: Pimpla albomarginata Cameron; B: P. caerulea Brullé; C: P. sumichrasti Cresson. Scale bars = 5.00 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3479051/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3479056>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3. A–D: Other Pimpla Fabricius species recorded for the study area (in vivo - lateral view): A: P. azteca Cresson; B: P. croceipes Cresson; C: P. flavipennis (Enderlein); D: P. platysma (Porter). Scale bars = 5.00 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3479056/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3479053>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2. A–M: Pimpla morphological structures. A–B: metasoma, dorsolateral view—arrows showing laterotergites V (modified from Díaz, 2000); C–G: ovipositor apex, lateral view (modified from Porter, 1970); H–K: tergite I, lateral view, female (modified from Porter, 1970); L–M: tergite I, lateral view, male (modified from Porter, 1970)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3479053/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

